summary:
Petrophysicist/Petroleum Engineer, 24 years experience in the industry.

Worked 14 years for various Shell operating companies. Ten years as petrophysical/petroleum engineering consultant based in the Netherlands and now for Vermilion Energy supporting European subsidiaries as Snr. Petrophysicst.

Specialties: Petrophysics, Hydrocarbon maturation studies
